T02TD2698E:66b-1: aa pa ri mi t'a yu ram sto tra /
T02TD2698E:66b-3: tshe dpag med la bstod pa /
T02TD2698E:66b-4: chos kyi 'khor lo rgya chen bskor //
T02TD2698E:66b-5: sems can sdug bsngal ma lus rnams //
T02TD2698E:66b-6: skad cig nyid la sel byed pa'i //
T02TD2698E:66b-7: sangs rgyas tshe dpag phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2698E:66b-8: rdo rje sems dpa' las byung zhing //
T02TD2698E:66b-9: nyes pa kun las khyod grol nas //
T02TD2698E:66b-10: rdo rje lus can rdo rje can //
T02TD2698E:66b-11: rdo rje tshe dpag phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2698E:66b-12: ji ltar nyon mongs dri ma yis //
T02TD2698E:66b-13: kun nas gos par mi 'gyur zhing //
T02TD2698E:66b-14: thugs rjes chags tshul ston mdzad pa //
T02TD2698E:66b-16: bsam pa dngos kun skad cig gis //
T02TD2698E:66b-17: rang 'dod bzhin du tshim dang dpal //
T02TD2698E:66b-18: tshogs kyi bdag po chen po ste //
T02TD2698E:66b-19: rin chen tshe dpag phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2698E:66b-20: 'dod pa'i don rnams ma lus pa //
T02TD2698E:66b-21: skad cig nyid la rdzogs dang dpal //
T02TD2698E:66b-22: bsam kun 'phel byed dpag bsam shing //
T02TD2698E:66b-23: phrin las tshe dpag phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2698E:66b-24: nyes pa kun las rnam grol bas //
T02TD2698E:66b-25: sna tshogs yon tan rnams kyis brgyan //
T02TD2698E:66b-26: tshogs kyi bdag po chen po ste //
T02TD2698E:66b-27: kun gzigs tshe dpag phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2698E:66b-28: stobs chen rnams kyis rab brgyan te //
T02TD2698E:66b-29: ma lus mi mthun tshogs 'joms pa / ston pa sred med bu yi mthu //
T02TD2698E:66b-30: yon tan tshe dpag phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2698E:66b-31: me long mnyam nyid la sogs pa //
T02TD2698E:66b-32: ye shes mang po'i mdzod 'dzin pa //
T02TD2698E:66b-33: rnam par rtog pa mtha' dag spangs //
T02TD2698E:66b-34: ye shes tshe dpag phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2698E:66b-35: rnam rtog rlung gis khyod mi g-yo //
T02TD2698E:67a-2: bdud dang mu stegs tshogs 'joms pa //
T02TD2698E:67a-3: mi g-yo tshe dpag phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2698E:67a-4: 'khor ba'i sems can thams cad kyis //
T02TD2698E:67a-6: tshe dang ye shes rgyas mdzad pa //
T02TD2698E:67a-7: tshe dpag med la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2698E:67a-8: byang chub sems dpa' dze t'a ri dgra las rnam par rgyal bas mdzad pa'o //
T02TD2698E:67a-11: grub pa brnyes pa'i snyid po zhabs //
T02TD2698E:67a-12: dze t'a ri dgra las rnam par rgyal ba //
T02TD2698E:67a-13: rdo rje gdan pa che chung gnyis //
T02TD2698E:67a-19: bla ma bsam gtan bzang po'o//
